    "how_to_get": "Open a ticket on HelloMoon Discord, or visit https://hellomoon.readme.io/reference/get-your-api-key, or get your API key by messaging our Telegram bot at https://t.me/lunar_lander_status_bot",
    "auth_scheme": "bearer (HTTP Bearer for some endpoints), query param for Lunar Lander"
  },
